[B][SIZE=3]Yes, this is the same old OS Prime that I used to run a couple months ago. It's been re-opened by a couple of old members and I have decided to re-join the development team. I am looking to bring it back to its peak again, and better it more than it ever was before. Note that your character files are not in tact considering there are new owners and the character files were never sold (of course), but everything else is still there - the gameplay and the atmosphere that we've all missed. So spill no more time, and re-join OS Prime![/SIZE][/B][/CENTER]
